3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the semantic quality of word vectors. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper uses neural network-based models for evaluation. 
5. cs.SD (Sound) is the least likely category as the paper does not deal with any aspect of sound or audio processing.
